name: Widyutkarali
description:
Goddess Widyutkarali is another name for Goddess Durga
    In the snippet of Sutasoma's story, it is told that the Goddess Widyutkarali appeared in a frightening and shocking form,
then the goddess changed her form to be beautiful and respectfully knelt before the prince Sutasoma who meditates and succeeds in conquering all passions and has a heart full of compassion. The goddess bestowed a spell called "Mahahrdayadharani", which was able to destroy all kinds of evil and ensure that mankind is freed from all kinds of diseases and misfortunes.
